data.description: Character and charm abound in this beautiful home in the desirable Irongate community.  This home features a brand new roof, custom cabinets and granite in the kitchen, fresh paint throughout entire home, cathedral ceilings in the family room and a cozy woodburning fireplace. It sits on a large corner, fenced in lot. There are 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. Half bath is downstais. Don't forget the location!  You will find this home close to grocery stores, restaurants, Summerville Medical Center and more. Washer, dryer and refrigerator convey with acceptable offer. A $1,300 Lender Credit is available and will be applied towards the buyer's closing costs and pre-paids if the buyer chooses to use the seller's preferred lender. Thiscredit is in addition to any negotiated seller concessions.
